140cms is a Twitter driven CMS.

Use assigned hash tags to assign tweets as content for your website.

See it in action at jamus.co.uk/140cms
---------------------------------

_Installation
Simply install files on server.
Ensure includes/functions.php has write permissions

_Updating Tweets
Set up a Cron job of your server to load includes/functions.php


